{"tid":156911,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"棒球大聯盟2 88 吾郎回歸","createTime":"2017-03-15T05:44:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T07:20:56.000Z","uid":33539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a6bff67c5dc3f0ae04d294e1a60df124ee2c86f3","tid":156911,"uid":33539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T05:44:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tieba.baidu.com/p/5007215251\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftieba.baidu.com%2Fp%2F5007215251&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=4797b4c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://tieba.baidu.com/p/5007215251</a><br />\n畫撚左成年半先比返老牌人物出場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a794a67008511faeef000919d3013009e38fb710","tid":156911,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T06:57:48.000Z","msg":"睇到三十幾話漫畫人就無update<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ae3ad2385a9e0b8d83e315f2b707276c079a7a","tid":156911,"uid":21514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T07:06:20.000Z","msg":"食完老本再食老本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ad9d0d4c0b54fc7f209bc301ed297ed3ecf62e","tid":156911,"uid":33539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T07:56:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇到三十幾話漫畫人就無update<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n劇情垃圾到冇人譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecbec7f4c86539c05f13a85fcc22440a3af3d305","tid":156911,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T08:10:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇到三十幾話漫畫人就無update<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n劇情垃圾到冇人譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過就算係無印major我都覺得麻麻地懶熱血<br />\n由細到大話要做職棒球員<br />\n小學有傷都夾硬要投結果廢咗右手<br />\n高中入到名校又屎忽痕走去退學浪費一年<br />\n同埋又係有傷夾硬要投球(雖然係海堂條仆街搞事)<br />\n畢業唔靠後父去美國挑戰自己呢part ok <br />\n但事業起步發現自己有傷(血行阻礙)又當無野夾硬投球<br />\n完全無吸收到自己廢右手嘅經歷<br />\n如果唔係有gibson 醒目,吾郎條on9仔遲早街頭棒球都打唔到"},{"pid":"55326c86156b53197284d975a2856b0156b79349","tid":156911,"uid":36915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T10:25:49.000Z","msg":"點都好過乜9鑽石王牌畫左十鳩幾年都未做冠軍<br />\n56已經係世界冠軍"},{"pid":"0df08df7673eb862e773cb340f197b9d0c5bbbd9","tid":156911,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T10:36:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點都好過乜9鑽石王牌畫左十鳩幾年都未做冠軍<br />\n56已經係世界冠軍</blockquote><br />\n咪玩啦<br />\nMajor 出咗成60期書先做到世界冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84dbc4f422734c37ffe50d816abad8ba40791ab2","tid":156911,"uid":33539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T11:48:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點都好過乜9鑽石王牌畫左十鳩幾年都未做冠軍<br />\n56已經係世界冠軍</blockquote><br />\n一套著重高中棒球<br />\n一套著重刻畫主角一生既棒球生涯冇得咁比既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647021c5044824fa6380704d07010703385cbc3b","tid":156911,"uid":33539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:25:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f60666064f41cf6a78e51f4d30f88f09de971392","tid":156911,"uid":1453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:44:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點都好過乜9鑽石王牌畫左十鳩幾年都未做冠軍<br />\n56已經係世界冠軍</blockquote><br />\n咪玩啦<br />\nMajor 出咗成60期書先做到世界冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係79期咩"},{"pid":"27409bdb34a491e1147d6087e8bd296ae720b8d3","tid":156911,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15